17. A kit for preventing for preventing a pregnancy or preventing a sexually transmitted disease comprising: 
(a) a unit dose form of an activated carbon; 
(b) a unit dose form of an spermicidal agent, an anti-sexually transmitted disease agent, or mixtures thereof; 
(c) a package containing components (a) and (b); and 
(d) optionally directions for use thereof.

18. A kit for preventing for preventing a pregnancy or preventing a sexually transmitted disease comprising: 
(a) a unit dose form of an activated carbon; 
(b) a barrier agent; 
(c) a package containing components (a) and (b); and optionally directions for use thereof.
